name: Catch The Crow
description:
Catch The Crow Is A Game Where You Play As A Net Named Netty.

Use The Arrow Keys To Move Netty.

To Win You Have To Get 100 Points By Collect The Flying Creatures In The Game, With Help From The Yellow Double Jump Power Up You Can Do It!

Crow = 1 Point.

Bat = -10 Points.

Eagle = 10 Points.

It Is Fun.
